---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet"
	pubDate={new Date()}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>Last updated: May 2026</p>

	<hr />

	<p>
		SQMUSIC is a music project that explores different sounds, styles, and emotions through sound.
	</p>

	<p>
		Started in 2023, the project focuses on experimenting with genres — from energetic and experimental tracks to more melodic and atmospheric vibes.
	</p>

	<p>
		Each release is created with a simple idea: sound should feel alive and different every time.
	</p>

	<p>
		SQMUSIC was originally founded in France, but at the moment it is not fixed to a specific location and is still deciding where it will be based in the future.
	</p>

	<p>
		The project continues to grow across platforms like SoundCloud, TikTok, Instagram, and others, building its own creative identity.
	</p>

	<hr />

	<p><strong>SQMUSIC RECORDS</strong></p>

	<p>
		SQMUSIC RECORDS is a label founded in mid-2024.
	</p>

	<p>
		It is currently under development and being shaped into a platform that will support future releases and creative projects.
	</p>

	<hr />

	<p><strong>NEW WORK</strong></p>

	<p>
		New tracks, ideas, and experiments are constantly in progress.
	</p>
</Layout>
	<p>

	</p>
</Layout>
